---
---

<section id="about" class="relative py-24 md:py-40 px-6 md:px-12 bg-sage texture-grain texture-flour" data-section="about">
  <!-- Wheat Divider Top -->
  <div class="divider-wheat mb-16 md:mb-24">
    <span class="text-script text-xl text-cream/50">our story</span>
  </div>

  <!-- Section Label -->
  <div class="mb-16 md:mb-24">
    <span class="text-label text-cream/60">02 — Origin</span>
  </div>

  <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-12 md:gap-20">
    <!-- Left: Image -->
    <div class="w-full md:w-[40%]">
      <div class="relative aspect-[3/4] overflow-hidden rounded-sm">
        <img
          src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1517433367423-c7e5b0f35086?w=800&q=80"
          alt="Baker's hands kneading fresh dough on a flour-dusted wooden surface"
          class="w-full h-full object-cover"
          loading="lazy"
        />
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-sage/30 to-transparent"></div>
      </div>
      <!-- Hand-drawn caption -->
      <p class="text-script text-lg text-cream/50 mt-4 text-center">crafted with care, every single day</p>
    </div>

    <!-- Right: Editorial Copy -->
    <div class="w-full md:w-[55%] md:ml-auto flex flex-col justify-center">
      <h2 class="text-display-lg italic mb-4 md:mb-6">Our Story</h2>
      <div class="underline-hand inline-block mb-10 md:mb-16 w-48"></div>

      <div class="max-w-xl space-y-6">
        <p class="text-lg md:text-xl leading-relaxed text-cream/90">
          <span class="font-display text-6xl md:text-7xl italic float-left mr-3 mt-1 leading-[0.8] text-gold">B</span>akes
          Bay was born from a simple belief — that every bite should feel like an occasion. Nestled along the
          quiet stretch of Maruthamalai Road in Coimbatore, we set out to craft baked goods, beverages, and desserts
          that don't just satisfy a craving but create a moment worth remembering.
        </p>

        <p class="text-base leading-relaxed text-cream/70">
          From our ovens come golden croissants and crusty sourdough loaves each morning. Our signature Royal
          Falooda — a towering celebration of rose, vermicelli, and hand-churned ice cream — sits alongside
          freshly muddled mojitos, creamy lassis, and pastries that melt on the tongue.
        </p>

        <!-- Pull Quote -->
        <blockquote class="border-l-2 border-gold/50 pl-6 py-4 my-10">
          <p class="text-script text-2xl md:text-3xl text-cream leading-snug">
            "We don't just bake. We make the quiet moments between conversations a little sweeter."
          </p>
        </blockquote>

        <p class="text-base leading-relaxed text-cream/70">
          What started as a neighbourhood bakery has become Coimbatore's destination for those who
          believe that a well-made croissant is a form of art, a perfect falooda is a celebration, and
          the best conversations happen over something freshly baked.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
